        <mxCell id="id8GIDBzt5Ycg5tB8IS--22" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tasks:&lt;/b&gt; Clustering, dimensionality reduction, anomaly detection, generative models.&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;strokeWidth=0.5;fillColor=#FFF4C3;strokeColor=#934900;container=0;fontSize=10;fontStyle=0;fontFamily=Mali;spacingLeft=2;align=left;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DMali;" parent="id8GIDBzt5Ycg5tB8IS--6" vertex="1">
